tagline: Wildfire Management Tools and NASA World Wind projects
body:
### [WorldWindExplorer](https://github.com/emxsys/WorldWindExplorer)
The World Wind Explorer is a geo-browser web app framework based on the [NASA Web World Wind SDK](https://github.com/NASAWorldWind/WebWorldWind).  This is an HTML5 web app built with Knockout and Bootstrap libraries.

### Authors and Contributors
Emxsys projects are authored by Bruce Schubert (@emxsys)
